{"tid":1565893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] 三個月後 大家係咪已經唔記得咗天琦講過咩？","createTime":"2019-09-13T10:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T21:25:45.000Z","uid":257516,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"28543467c38496d7ecfc0311440078e05ed8c3fd","tid":1565893,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:23:52.000Z","msg":"逆權運動已經嚟到第三個月 實在唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先請大家J吓勇武BB先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttLChZE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttLChZE.gif&h=8b10d9a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n勇武全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bfX6O3t.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbfX6O3t.gif&h=5576e96a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7q4AMD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7q4AMD.gif&h=b63c320a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1212 打狗 救人 1212 打狗 救人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rwBn607.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrwBn607.gif&h=eac4c43c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vwzw0e6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVwzw0e6.gif&h=00e3fdab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFOdu04.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFOdu04.gif&h=49147452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打狗棒法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c5Vj9b0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc5Vj9b0.gif&h=d405a3a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黨衛軍：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FmALhfW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFmALhfW.gif&h=09f60535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要多謝勇武 還香港各區一片寧靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家終於喺禮拜六日去尖咀都唔會俾喼碌親<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇勇武 亦唔會換到最初「暫緩」兩隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVEUhAVki0DA&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4Qa0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=8e463afc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA</a><br />\n百聽不厭 每次聽都有新體會<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家記住「不割席 不分化 不督灰」唔係一句口號 而係我哋成功嘅關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/767011fddc78523e965c2abc2f47496f/5DFD206F/t51.2885-15/sh0.08/e35/c2.0.740.740a/s640x640/67798257_503014147122119_5528630371514866904_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=111\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F767011fddc78523e965c2abc2f47496f%2F5DFD206F%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fsh0.08%2Fe35%2Fc2.0.740.740a%2Fs640x640%2F67798257_503014147122119_5528630371514866904_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D111&h=433b62a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係 呢句唔係遮醜布 眼見有唔少手足對善意批評都好激動 甚至郁啲就話係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以請大家亦記住「不完美，可接受，要改善」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天琦講過 大家應該要摒棄教條主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//<em>過往我地成日強調話 我地要勇武抗爭 我地唾棄形式主義 唾棄失敗主義 <br />\n咁係咪代表我地一定唔可以嗌口號 唔可以搞遊行 唔可以搞集會 唔可以聽歌呢 ?</em><br />\n<strong>其實一直都唔係！</strong> //<br />\n<br />\n//<em>我地反對嘅係教條主義 而唔係和平集會或者公民抗命本身嘅能力</em>//<br />\n冇錯 可能大家覺得呢幾日淨係喺商場唱願榮光歸香港 好左膠feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(利申 我都覺)<br />\n又話冇俾對家狙擊 方向錯曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n的確 淨係唱歌就可以推翻呢個政權咩？人唔笑狗都吠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話要將抗爭嘉年華化 但係 家下只係平日夜晚食完飯一個紓壓活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家真係唔駛咁著緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n況且禮拜六日keep住有event 加上之前打算起大台嘅垃圾都已經屌走咗 現階段我都幾肯定班垃圾唔撚敢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//<em>條條大路通羅馬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊一個方式可以推翻呢一個政府嘅 呢一個方式就應該要去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em>//<br />\n<br />\n致和理非<br />\n你哋一直都係勇武最強大嘅後盾 冇咗你哋 運動係無可能可以維持到今時今日<br />\n任憑對家出盡奶力分化你哋 你哋選擇咗同舊時嘅你say bye bye<br />\n將不割席 不分化 不督灰發揮到極致<br />\n<br />\n不過 近排啲文宣真係少咗好多文宣 同運動早期海量airdrop 滿天七彩繽紛poster真係有一段距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更有唔少人真心覺得手足們跳閘係為咗慳錢/搭霸王車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要記住 跳閘係為咗抗議黨鐵721 831置市民安危於死地 當中831更大開中門俾警犬入站無差別攻擊市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話 和理非參考對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/DampFlickeringAmurstarfish-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FDampFlickeringAmurstarfish-size_restricted.gif&h=820a32c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//相信和平抗爭嘅人 相信公民抗命嘅人 繼續公民抗命<br />\n相信佔馬路 相信絕食 相信罷交稅等等唔同和平手段嘅人 繼續去做<br />\n我鼓勵你地去做 我希望你地去做<br />\n我唔希望因為有人批評你地嘅手段 結果就完全放棄你地相信嘅野<br />\n同時間相信勇武抗爭嘅人 一樣都要繼續做//<br />\n<br />\n//我地反抗政府 攞返我哋應有權力嘅時候 我哋要因時制宜<br />\n當晚有近千個警察守係西環 如果我哋盲目相信勇武抗爭係一定會成功 只有勇武抗爭係一定要行嘅路嘅話 我地當晚就會一齊去送死<br />\n我唔想見有人犧牲 亦都唔想見到有人係被推上前線<br />\n只係喺一個必需嘅情況底下 只係喺一個兩難嘅局面 <br />\n一係就留低 一係就企喺度抵抗嘅時候 <br />\n我哋先至要孤注一擲 勇武抗爭！<br />\n我希望大家明白呢一點 唔好再繼續教條主義 <strong>唔好再盲目相信自己嘅果一條道路係一定會成功</strong><br />\n係必須要行嘅道路<br />\n而其他所有嘅道路,都係唔應該行 <strong>係錯嘅</strong>//<br />\n<br />\n以下我唔係想各打五十大板 懶係公正咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但無論和理非定勇武都要記住：<br />\n<strong>唔好再盲目相信自己嘅果一條道路係一定會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n天琦會喺10月9號上訴 各位可唔可以過嚟聲援吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 光復香港 時代革命<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, the Revolution of Our Times<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\nFive Demands Not One Less<br />\n<br />\nGive me democracy or give me DEATH<br />\n<br />\nSI VIS PACEM<br />\nPARA BELLUM<br />\n祝大家武運昌隆<br />\n<br />\n勇武寶寶可唔可以唔好咁cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GHt8Zuk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGHt8Zuk.gif&h=d3f01643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b7d8f466ae221c77ceb2c81079cef07e8bea8fab","tid":1565893,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:24:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月15日見！</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Trzyi1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrzyi1f.jpg&h=f89f6e65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21e35b271ada74cf179a778576c2caf73c4ce39f","tid":1565893,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:24:52.000Z","msg":"黨衛軍小心暴斃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tzfhVG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tzfhVG.gif&h=e6c40422&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d449a8062034b8f2aac699b9dd8a924f2c43db7","tid":1565893,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"多行不義必自斃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHxyuqp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHxyuqp.gif&h=98a775ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"533e916caecb1d7929880d07b95f8bd69ed3abca","tid":1565893,"uid":257516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:29:29.000Z","msg":"2017 連登仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W67hz0A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW67hz0A.jpg&h=102f5871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019 連登仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2017AX6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2017AX6.jpg&h=6df22810&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bbce4be48897257fd6337e24049eabc1e806d09","tid":1